All the cadres and masses of various ethnic groups in Xinjiang are greatly delighted in celebrating the 60th anniversary of Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region with full passions. And the painters from Makit county of Kashi prefecture, also the Home of Farmers' Paintings , created 60 pictures depicting the inspiring changes and happy life around themselves, presenting a special gift for the occasion. From today on, Tianshannet will launch a special exhibition online, focusing on these pictures and sharing their joy at the moment.
Gratitude to the great motherland, Endeavor to build a better home
